            <note xml:id="foot.f2">CD referred to <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_4650.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Le Couteur 1836</ref> (<hi rend="italic">On the varieties, properties, and classification of wheat</hi>) in <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_7951.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Variation</hi></ref> 1: 314–18 and 2: 203.</note>
